T15TD4342E:155b-0: @155b # // na mo lo ke shva ra ye /
T15TD4342E:155b-1: shing bzo bas grub pa thob pa ni /
T15TD4342E:155b-2: dza ga ta lar gar log byung ba'i tshe mi rnams kyis shar phyogs bham ga lar bros so //
T15TD4342E:155b-3: lam ka na shing bzo ba'i bu cig yod pas mthong nas bros pa'i dge 'dun rnams la brkyang phyag btsal zhabs spyi bor blangs /
T15TD4342E:155b-5: der de ltar byas pa'i rgyu mtshan dris pas /
T15TD4342E:155b-6: de na re bdag gi pha dad pa che bas /
T15TD4342E:155b-7: rab byung cig la bsnyen bkur byas /
T15TD4342E:155b-8: des kyang thugs rje chen po'i sgom bzlas phog nas nyams su blangs /
T15TD4342E:155b-9: dus ring zhig na nad kyis btab nas shi ste dur khrod du shing brtsigs te dkyil du bcug nas mtha' nas me sbar ba dang thon byung /
T15TD4342E:155b-10: der dris pas nga khyim du theg bshad do zhes zer ro //
T15TD4342E:155b-12: nga gshin rje'i skyes bu shin tu 'jigs pa bzhis khyer nas dmyal ba'i gnas su bkum pa na ra ka'i nang mes gang bar bcug pa dang /
T15TD4342E:155b-13: der bkum pa na ra ka kha zum nas ma tshud phyir bskyed pa dang /
T15TD4342E:155b-15: yang yang de bzhin du byung bas skyes bu bzhi po 'jigs nas gshin rje chos kyi rgyal po la dris pas /
T15TD4342E:155b-16: de na re 'dir skye ba'i rgyu zad thugs rje chen po'i bu yin da cig car skyol zhes zer nas bskyal ba dang nga'i nad drag 'dug ces zer ro //
T15TD4342E:155b-17: de phyir rab tu byung ba mthong tshad la brkyang phyag 'tshal zhing bsnyen bkur byed /
T15TD4342E:155b-18: bya ba thams cad bzhag nas sgom bzlas byed pa cig byung /
T15TD4342E:155b-19: bdag kyang pha'i rjes su bgyid pa lags zer ro //
T15TD4342E:155b-20: sngags pa kharsa p'a ni'i snying po bgrang ba cig la yang de kho na bzhin byung skad /
T15TD4342E:155b-21: shing bzo bas grub pa thob pa panti ta bi na ya shr'is bsgyur ro//
